snippet.title: Chernobylite console announcement trailer - PURE GAMEPLAY!
snippet.description:
Chernobylite console announcement trailer is our latest video which is connected to two important events: release of the Mega Patch number 7 (out of 8) and we finally can tell that version for both next-gen and current-gen consoles will also happen!

#Chernobylite #console #announcement
